# Keep host build artifacts out of the build context so Docker builds match a clean
# git clone (e.g. Dokploy/CI). Critically, excluding node_modules forces the image to
# rely on the deps stage's pnpm install rather than silently copying the dev tree's
# node_modules — which previously masked a missing-dependency bug in a local build.
**/node_modules
.git
**/.next
**/dist
**/.turbo
**/*.log
